  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. Cut chicken into 1-inch cubes and thread onto skewers.",
    "3. In a small bowl, mix together olive oil, Moroccan seasoning, salt, and black pepper.",
    "4. Brush the mixture onto both sides of the chicken.",
